            </summary>
            <div class="pdp-faq-a">
              <p><strong>30-day full refund. No return required.</strong> Email <a href="mailto:orders@livehappie.com">orders@livehappie.com</a> within 30 days for a full refund. Zero risk to try.</p>
            </div>
