          <details class="pdp-faq-item">
            <summary class="pdp-faq-q">
              <span class="pdp-faq-icon"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 8h1a4 4 0 0 1 0 8h-1"/><path d="M3 8h14v9a4 4 0 0 1-4 4H7a4 4 0 0 1-4-4V8z"/><line x1="6" y1="2" x2="6" y2="4"/><line x1="10" y1="2" x2="10" y2="4"/><line x1="14" y1="2" x2="14" y2="4"/></svg></span>
              <span>Is this like mushroom coffee (MUD\WTR, RYZE, Four Sigmatic)?</span>
              <span class="pdp-faq-chev"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></span>
