            </summary>
            <div class="pdp-faq-a">
              <p>Energy drinks spike. Happie sustains. <strong>Celsius has 200mg caffeine. Red Bull has 80mg. Happie has 0mg.</strong> Instead of stimulating your adrenals (which leads to the crash + dependency loop), Happie supports your body's own ATP production at the cellular level. You get the focused-alert feeling without the jitters, the post-3pm crash, or the disrupted sleep. Better cleaner energy that doesn't tank your tolerance over time.</p>
